extends ../../../../../app/views/layout-marketing

block content
  main#main-content.content.content-alt
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-6.offset-lg-3.col-xl-4.offset-xl-4
          .card
            .card-body
              .page-header
                h1 自助注册
              if success
                .alert.alert-success(role='alert')
                  if info
                    | #{info}
                  else
                    | 激活邮件已发送，请查收。
              if error
                .alert.alert-danger(role='alert')
                  | #{error}
              form(name='selfRegisterForm' action='/self-register' method='POST')
                input(type='hidden' name='_csrf' value=csrfToken)
                .form-group
                  label(for='emailField') 邮箱
                  input#emailField.form-control(
                    type='email'
                    name='email'
                    required
                    placeholder='email@example.com'
                    value=email
                    autocomplete='email'
                  )
                .actions
                  button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') 发送激活邮件
                p.text-muted.mt-3
                  | 填写邮箱后会收到一封设置密码的激活邮件。
